## Rules

- **Follow the plan** - Don't add features not in the plan
- **One task at a time** - Complete fully before moving on
- **Report deviations** - If you need to do something differently, explain why
- **Keep the plan updated** - It's the source of truth
- **Test as you go** - Don't wait until the end

